big__left x-tabs_list" role="tablist"><div class="brxe-div bd-mm-big__left-header"><h2 class="brxe-heading bd-mm-big__left-title">Services</h2></div><div class="brxe-divider bd-mm-big__line horizontal"><div class="line"></div></div><ul class="brxe-div list--none bd-mm-big__list"><li class="brxe-rdfcua brxe-div bd-mm-big__tab-item x-tabs_tab" role="tab" data-brx-loop-start="rdfcua"><span class="brxe-idzffv brxe-text-basic bd-mm-big__tab-item-title">Investment Attraction</span><i class="fas fa-circle-arrow-right brxe-ptlqqj brxe-icon bd-mm-big__tab-item-icon"></i></li><li class="brxe-rdfcua brxe-div bd-mm-big__tab-item x-tabs_tab" role="tab"><span class="brxe-idzffv brxe-text-basic bd-mm-big__tab-item-title">Strategy &#038; Consulting</span><i class="fas fa-circle-arrow-right brxe-ptlqqj brxe-icon bd-mm-big__tab-item-icon"></i></li><li class="brxe-rdfcua brxe-div bd-mm-big__tab-item x-tabs_tab" role="tab"><span class="brxe-idzffv brxe-text-basic bd-mm-big__tab-item-title">Investment Attraction Training</span><i class="fas fa-circle-arrow-right brxe-ptlqqj brxe-icon bd-mm-big__tab-item-icon"></i></li><li class="brxe-rdfcua brxe-div bd-mm-big__tab-item x-tabs_tab" role="tab"><span class="brxe-idzffv brxe-text-basic bd-mm-big__tab-item-title">Trade &#038; Export</span><i class="fas fa-circle-arrow-right brxe-ptlqqj brxe-icon bd-mm-big__tab-item-icon"></i></li><li class="brxe-rdfcua brxe-div bd-mm-big__tab-item x-tabs_tab" role="tab"><span class="brxe-idzffv brxe-text-basic bd-mm-big__tab-item-title">FDI365</span><i class="fas fa-circle-arrow-right brxe-ptlqqj brxe-icon bd-mm-big__tab-item-icon"></i></li><li class="brxe-rdfcua brxe-div bd-mm-big__tab-item x-tabs_tab" role="tab"><span class="brxe-idzffv brxe-text-basic bd-mm-big__tab-item-title">Corporate Services</span><i class="fas fa-circle-arrow-right brxe-ptlqqj brxe-icon bd-mm-big__tab-item-icon"></i></li><li class="brx-query-trail" data-query-element-id="rdfcua" data-query-vars="{&quot;post_type&quot;:[&quot;service&quot;],&quot;orderby&quot;:{&quot;menu_order&quot;:&quot;ASC&quot;},&quot;posts_per_page&quot;:6,&quot;post__not_in&quot;:[&quot;5315&quot;,&quot;6270&quot;],&quot;post_status&quot;:&quot;publish&quot;,&quot;paged&quot;:1}" data-page="1" data-max-pages="1" data-start="1" data-end="6"></li></ul></div><div id="brxe-iabuxa" class="brxe-block bd-mm-big__right x-tabs_content"><div class="brxe-oxbvxd brxe-block bd-mm-big__tab-content-item x-tabs_content-item" data-brx-loop-start="oxbvxd"><div class="brxe-eifmzb brxe-block bd-mm-big__tab-content-item__tab-panel x-tabs_panel" role="tabpanel"><div class="brxe-acrshj brxe-block bd-mm-big__tab-content-item__tab-content x-tabs_panel-content"><div class="brxe-jjdojn brxe-block bd-mm-big__tab-content"><h3 class="brxe-izcqdv brxe-heading bd-mm-big__tab-content-item__heading">Investment Attraction</h3><div class="brxe-xkjvsz brxe-text bd-mm-big__tab-content-item__text"><p><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>
<p>Our Investment Attraction Services empower economic development organizations and investment promotion agencies to attract high-value investments through targeted strategies and expert support.</p>
<p>Lead Generation Programs connect you with quality leads by leveraging research-driven campaigns at international tradeshows, virtual programs, and in-market missions.</p>
<p>Prospect Database Development can enhance your outreach with tailored databases of high-growth companies that align with your region’s target sectors.</p>
<p>In-Market Representation service provides access to experienced consultants who act as an extension of your team, expanding your reach during international visits and investment missions.</p>
<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --></p>
</div><a class="brxe-nqqbts brxe-button bd-mm-big__tab-content-item__button btn--primary bricks-button bricks-background-primary" href="https://researchfdi.com/service/investment-attraction/">Explore this service</a><div class="brxe-gxenpw brxe-divider bd-mm-big__line horizontal"><div class="line"></div></div><ul class="brxe-xztcav brxe-block list--none bd-mm-big__sub-list"><li class="brxe-psurwe brxe-div bd-mm-big__sub-list-item" data-brx-loop-start="psurwe"><i class="ti-star brxe-nstkzw brxe-icon bd-mm__grid-item-icon"></i><div class="brxe-itposb brxe-div bd-mm__grid-item-content"><h5 class="brxe-qmlruq brxe-heading bd-mm__grid-item-content__heading clickable-parent">Lead Generation Programs</h5><p class="brxe-uwlfys brxe-text-basic bd-mm__grid-item-content__text">Unlock investment opportunities with targeted research and global outreach.</p></div></li><li class="brxe-psurwe brxe-div bd-mm-big__sub-list-item"><i class="ti-star brxe-nstkzw brxe-icon bd-mm__grid-item-icon"></i><div class="brxe-itposb brxe-div bd-mm__grid-item-content"><h5 class="brxe-qmlruq brxe-heading bd-mm__grid-item-content__heading clickable-parent">Prospect Database Development</h5><p class="brxe-uwlfys brxe-text-basic bd-mm__grid-item-content__text">Dial in your outreach with custom databases of high-growth companies.</p></div></li><li class="brxe-psurwe brxe-div bd-mm-big__sub-list-item"><i class="ti-star brxe-nstkzw brxe-icon bd-mm__grid-item-icon"></i><div class="brxe-itposb brxe-div bd-mm__grid-item-content"><h5 class="brxe-qmlruq brxe-heading bd-mm__grid-item-content__heading clickable-parent">In-Market Representation</h5><p class="brxe-uwlfys brxe-text-basic bd-mm__grid-item-content__text">Tap into expert consultants supporting your investment efforts.</p></div></li><li class="brx-query-trail" data-query-element-id="psurwe" data-query-vars="[]" data-page="1" data-max-pages="1" data-start="0" data-end="0"></li></ul></div><li class="brxe-nomaqg brxe-block bd-mm-related-card" data-brx-loop-start="nomaqg"><div class="brxe-ktppgc brxe-div bd-mm-related-card__media-wrapper"><figure class="brxe-pruiae brxe-image bd-mm-related-card__media tag"><picture class="css-filter size-medium_large" loading="eager" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high">
<source type="image/webp" srcset="https://researchfdi.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/corpus-christi-texas-768x512.jpg.webp 768w, https://researchfdi.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/corpus-christi-texas-300x200.jpg.webp 300w, https://researchfdi.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/corpus-christi-texas-1024x682.jpg.webp 1024w, https://researchfdi.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/corpus-christi-texas-1536x1024.jpg.webp 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px"/>
<img width="768" height="512" src="https://researchfdi.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/corpus-christi-texas-768x512.jpg" alt="Featured image of Lead Generation Success Stories with Team Texas" loading="eager" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://researchfdi.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/corpus-christi-texas-768x512.jpg 768w, https://researchfdi.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/corpus-christi-texas-300x200.jpg 300w, https://researchfdi.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/corpus-christi-texas-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https://researchfdi.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/corpus-christi-texas-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://researchfdi.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/corpus-christi-texas.jpg 1919w" sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px"/>
</picture>
</figure></div><div class="brxe-evhpkw brxe-div bd-mm-related-card__content-wrapper"><h4 class="brxe-hmvyhz brxe-heading clickable-parent bd-mm-related-card__heading"><a href="https://researchfdi.com/case-study/researchfdis-lead-generation-success-stories-with-team-texas/">Team Texas</a></h4><p class="brxe-gtrbsr brxe-text-basic bd-mm-related-card__lede">ResearchFDI, in partnership with Team Texas, has played a pivotal role in driving investment attraction...</p><p class="brxe-jrvptk brxe-text-basic fr-accent-heading fr-intro-alpha__accent-heading bd-mm-related-card__accent-heading">Featured Case Study</p><div class="brxe-dkaelz brxe-div fr-cta-links-alpha bd-mm-related-card__cta-links-alpha"><span class="brxe-rhqvdo brxe-button btn--primary bd-mm-related-card__primary-action btn--s bricks-button bricks-background-primary">Read case study</span></div></div></li><li class="brx-query-trail" data-query-element-id="nomaqg" data-query-vars="[]" data-page="1" data-max-pages="1" data-start="0" data-end="0"></li></div></div></div><div class="brxe-oxbvxd brxe-block bd-mm-big__tab-content-item x-tabs_content-item"><div class="brxe-eifmzb brxe-block bd-mm-big__tab-content-item__tab-panel x-tabs_panel" role="tabpanel"><div class="brxe-acrshj brxe-block bd-mm-big__tab-content-item__tab-content x-tabs_panel-content"><div class="brxe-jjdojn brxe-block bd-mm-big__tab-content"><h3 class="brxe-izcqdv brxe-heading bd-mm-big__tab-content-item__heading">Strategy &#038; Consulting</h3><div class="brxe-xkjvsz brxe-text bd-mm-big__tab-content-item__text"><p>Our Strategy &amp; Consulting services provide economic development organizations and investment promotion agencies with data-driven insights and tailored roadmaps to attract inward investments and foster long-term growth.</p>
<p>Comprehensive studies—including market analysis, sector prioritization, and benchmarking—offer a clear understanding of where your region stands and how to leverage its strengths. With customized Action Plans, we guide your region through actionable steps to secure high-value investments and enhance your competitive edge.</p>
<p>Whether you need to reprioritize your target industries, identify target markets, or craft a compelling value proposition, our strategic services equip your region with the tools to attract domestic and foreign inward investment and drive economic development.</p>
</div><a class="brxe-nqqbts brxe-button bd-mm-big__tab-content-item__button btn--primary bricks-button bricks-background-primary" href="https://researchfdi.com/service/strategy-consulting/">Explore this service</a><div class="brxe-gxenpw brxe-divider bd-mm-big__line horizontal"><div class="line"></div></div><ul class="brxe-xztcav brxe-block list--none bd-mm-big__sub-list"><li class="brxe-psurwe brxe-div bd-mm-big__sub-list-item" data-brx-loop-start="psurwe"><i class="ti-star brxe-nstkzw brxe-icon bd-mm__grid-item-icon"></i><div class="brxe-itposb brxe-div bd-mm__grid-item-content"><h5 class="brxe-qmlruq brxe-heading bd-mm__grid-item-content__heading clickable-parent">Market Study</h5><p class="brxe-uwlfys brxe-text-basic bd-mm__grid-item-content__text">Uncover new investment opportunities through market analysis.</p></div></li><li class="brxe-psurwe brxe-div bd-mm-big__sub-list-item"><i class="ti-star brxe-nstkzw brxe-icon bd-mm__grid-item-icon"></i><div class="brxe-itposb brxe-div bd-mm__grid-item-content"><h5 class="brxe-qmlruq brxe-heading bd-mm__grid-item-content__heading clickable-parent">Action/FDI Plan</h5><p class="brxe-uwlfys brxe-text-basic bd-mm__grid-item-content__text">Tailored roadmap with actionable steps for investment success.</p></div></li><li class="brxe-psurwe brxe-div bd-mm-big__sub-list-item"><i class="ti-star brxe-nstkzw brxe-icon bd-mm__grid-item-icon"></i><div class="brxe-itposb brxe-div bd-mm__grid-item-content"><h5 class="brxe-qmlruq brxe-heading bd-mm__grid-item-content__heading clickable-parent">Sector Study</h5><p class="brxe-uwlfys brxe-text-basic bd-mm__grid-item-content__text">Deep dive into industry dynamics and growth drivers.</p></div></li><li class="brx-query-trail" data-query-element-id="psurwe" data-query-vars="[]" data-page="1" data-max-pages="1" data-start="0" data-end="0"></li></ul></div><li class="brxe-nomaqg brxe-block bd-mm-related-card" data-brx-loop-start="nomaqg"><div class="brxe-ktppgc brxe-div bd-mm-related-card__media-wrapper"><figure class="brxe-pruiae brxe-image bd-mm-related-card__media tag"><img width="768" height="465" src="https://researchfdi.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/shutterstock_2311048099-scaled-e1755285624292-768x465.jpg" class="css-filter size-medium_large" alt="Featured image of Private: Central SC Alliance: Sharpening Investment Focus with Strategic Market Intelligence" loading="eager" decoding="async" srcset="https://researchfdi.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/shutterstock_2311048099-scaled-e1755285624292-768x465.jpg 768w, https://researchfdi.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/shutterstock_2311048099-scaled-e1755285624292-300x182.jpg 300w, https://researchfdi.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/shutterstock_2311048099-scaled-e1755285624292-1024x620.jpg 1024w, https://researchfdi.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/shutterstock_2311048099-scaled-e1755285624292.jpg 1515w" sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px" /></figure></div><div class="brxe-evhpkw brxe-div bd-mm-related-card__content-wrapper"><h4 class="brxe-hmvyhz brxe-heading clickable-parent bd-mm-related-card__heading"><a href="https://researchfdi.com/?post_type=case-study&#038;p=6796">Central SC Alliance</a></h4><p class="brxe-gtrbsr brxe-text-basic bd-mm-related-card__lede">In 2023, Central SC Alliance partnered with ResearchFDI to develop a customized FDI attraction strategy...</p><p class="brxe-jrvptk brxe-text-basic fr-accent-heading fr-intro-alpha__accent-heading bd-mm-related-card__accent-heading">Featured Case Study</p><div class="brxe-dkaelz brxe-div fr-cta-links-alpha bd-mm-related-card__cta-links-alpha"><span class="brxe-rhqvdo brxe-button btn--primary bd-mm-related-card__primary-action btn--s bricks-button bricks-background-primary">Read case study</span></div></div></li><li class="brx-query-trail" data-query-element-id="nomaqg" data-query-vars="[]" data-page="1" data-max-pages="1" data-start="0" data-end="0"></li></div></div></div><div class="brxe-oxbvxd brxe-block bd-mm-big__tab-content-item x-tabs_content-item"><div class="brxe-eifmzb brxe-block bd-mm-big__tab-content-item__tab-panel x-tabs_panel" role="tabpanel"><div class="brxe-acrshj brxe-block bd-mm-big__tab-content-item__tab-content x-tabs_panel-content"><div class="brxe-jjdojn brxe-block bd-mm-big__tab-content"><h3 class="brxe-izcqdv brxe-heading bd-mm-big__tab-content-item__heading">Investment Attraction Training</h3><div class="brxe-xkjvsz brxe-text bd-mm-big__tab-content-item__text"><p>Our Investment Attraction Training programs are designed to equip economic development professionals with the latest trends, tools, and best practices in investment attraction.</p>
<p>Combining in-person and virtual seminars with a flexible online learning platform, we offer targeted training that covers everything from lead generation to closing deals with key decision-makers. Our expert-led courses help regions enhance their ability to attract inward investments, generate high-quality leads, and position themselves for long-term success.</p>
<p>Whether you’re looking to upskill your team through interactive group exercises or gain certification through the ResearchFDI Academy, our adaptable programs can be tailored to meet the needs of organizations of all sizes, both public and private. With proven methodologies used by top investment promotion agencies worldwide, we ensure your team is equipped to navigate the complexities of investment promotion.</p>
</div><a class="brxe-nqqbts brxe-button bd-mm-big__tab-content-item__button btn--primary bricks-button bricks-background-primary" href="https://researchfdi.com/service/fdi-training/">Explore this service</a><div class="brxe-mxvfjq brxe-block bd-academy-cta-card-mm"><div class="brxe-tvrngd brxe-block bd-academy-cta-card__content-wrapper"><h2 class="brxe-tremmg brxe-heading bd-academy-cta-card__heading">Visit the ResearchFDI Academy Portal</h2><p class="brxe-bjycfo brxe-text-basic fr-accent-heading bd-academy-cta-card__accent-heading">Access Your Training Anytime</p><p class="brxe-wjpvih brxe-text-basic fr-lede bd-academy-cta-card__lede">Log in now to complete modules, track progress, and earn your certification.</p><a class="brxe-pfigtj brxe-button btn--primary bricks-button bricks-background-primary" href="https://researchfdi.com/service/fdi-training/researchfdi-academy/">Learn More</a></div><div class="brxe-rmqpgx brxe-block bd-academy-cta-card__media-wrapper"><figure class="brxe-ghvnrr brxe-image bd-academy-cta-card__media tag"><img src="https://researchfdi.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/researchfdi-academy.svg" class="css-filter size-full" alt="Abstract graphic depicting education and learning" decoding="async" /></figure></div></div></div><li class="brxe-nomaqg brxe-block bd-mm-related-card" data-brx-loop-start="nomaqg"><div class="brxe-ktppgc brxe-div bd-mm-related-card__media-wrapper"><figure class="brxe-pruiae brxe-image bd-mm-related-card__media tag"><picture class="css-filter size-medium_large" loading="eager" decoding="async">
