s="css-filter size-full" alt="ResearchFDI logo" decoding="async" loading="lazy" /></a></figure><div class="brxe-text fr-footer-alpha__description"><p>ResearchFDI is a Montreal, Canada-based lead generation, strategy, training, and business intelligence solutions providers. We help businesses and economic development organizations all around the world stay ahead of the competition and achieve sustainable economic growth.</p>
